If you fork/modify this scene, I request that you modify the graphics and the name too in order to make it clear that it's a different entity, unless of course you are fixing bugs. :) To me this scene is pretty much feature-complete now and I am not that interested in adding much more.

Please see the file TODO for a small list of things I want to add/fix.
